Duke of Wellington won the Battle of Waterloo on June 18 . 
  Model contains more than 30,000 figures and illustrates key moments of the battle . 
  It was built in the 1970s but fell into disrepair before being restored for the 200th anniversary . 
  The model has 21,500 soldiers and 10,000 horses on display at the Royal Green Jackets Museum in Winchester . 
 